OL,6,FOnce again, women across the UK are
OL,7,Fstruggling to secure their hormone
OL,8,Freplacement therapy (HRT) prescriptions
OL,9,Fas a fresh wave of shortages hits the
OL,10,Fcountry.
OL,12,FRoughly two million women in the UK
OL,13,Ftake HRT to help them deal with
OL,14,Fsymptoms caused by the menopause, which
OL,15,Fcan be severe. However, supply of the
OL,16,Fmedication has been beset by
OL,17,Fchallenges, with manufacturers
OL,18,Fseemingly failing to keep up with a
OL,19,Fgrowing demand for the treatment.
